      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a fixed-price quote</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-trust">
        <div><strong>60&ndash;120 min</strong>Storm callout, central shire</div>
        <div><strong>$1K&ndash;$15K</strong>Typical removal range</div>
        <div><strong>AS 4373</strong>Pruning standard, every job</div>
        <div><strong>$20M</strong>Public liability insurance</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2>Five things, done properly.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Tree removal, lopping &amp; pruning to AS 4373, stump grinding to
        replantable depth, 24/7 storm response, and full block clearing for
        build sites. No mowing, no hedging, no &ldquo;handyman&rdquo; work &mdash;
        just the chainsaw end of the trade, done by climbers who know what
        they&rsquo;re looking at.
      </p>

      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/tree-removal/">
          <div class="svc-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9876;</div>
          <h3>Tree removal</h3>
          <p>Full removal including stump. Climbed, sectional, EWP or spider-lift access for tight blocks. From a 6m wattle to a 30m blue gum next to powerlines. $800&ndash;$15,000.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See tree removal &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/tree-lopping/">
          <div class="svc-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9889;</div>
          <h3>Tree lopping &amp; pruning</h3>
          <p>Crown thinning, deadwooding, weight reduction, formative pruning, clearance pruning. AS 4373 compliant cuts. We don&rsquo;t &ldquo;top&rdquo; healthy trees. $300&ndash;$1,500.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See lopping &amp; pruning &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/stump-grinding/">
          <div class="svc-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9881;</div>
          <h3>Stump grinding</h3>
