          <span class="svc-link">See stump grinding &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/storm-response/">
          <div class="svc-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9888;</div>
          <h3>Storm response (24/7)</h3>
          <p>Tree on house, car, driveway or fence. Hung-up &ldquo;widow-maker&rdquo; limbs. 60&ndash;120 min response central shire, 24/7 every day of the year. Insurance docs provided. $400&ndash;$1,800.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See storm response &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/land-clearing/">
          <div class="svc-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9650;</div>
          <h3>Land clearing</h3>
